flowchart TB
    Sender([External SMTP])
    User([Webmail / IMAP Client])
    MX[MX Server<br/>+ Spam Filter<br/>SPF/DKIM/DMARC + ML]
    Relay[Outbound SMTP Relay<br/>+ Retry Queue]
    Meta[("Mailbox Metadata<br/>wide-column,<br/>sharded by user_id")]
    Blobs[("Content-Addressed<br/>Object Store<br/>SHA-256 dedup")]
    Index[("Per-User<br/>Search Index")]
    Notify[Push Notification<br/>Service]

    Sender -->|inbound| MX
    MX --> Meta
    MX --> Blobs
    MX -.->|index| Index
    MX -.->|push| Notify
    User -->|read / search| Meta
    Meta --> Blobs
    User -->|search query| Index
    User -->|send| Relay
    Relay -.->|MX lookup, deliver| Sender

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Sender,User external
    class MX,Relay,Notify service
    class Meta,Blobs,Index store
